headline: Keysight Joins Forces with the EU to Drive Innovation in 6G
summary: SANTA ROSA, Calif., February 11, 2025--Keysight Technologies, Inc. (NYSE: KEYS) is enhancing Europe’s 6G research and innovation landscape by participating in two projects that are a part of the 6G Smart Networks and Services Joint Undertaking (SNS-JU), a research and innovation program co-funded by the European Union (EU).
